%% Data Flow Diagram - Data Science Pipelines Operator
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP TLS (service-ca)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant APIServer as DS Pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant PipelinePod as Pipeline Pod<br/>(launcher/driver)
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant MariaDB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO<br/>9000/TCP or 443/TCP

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission (External User)
    User->>Router: POST /apis/v1beta1/pipelines<br/>HTTPS/443, OpenShift auth
    Router->>KRBAC: Reencrypt TLS<br/>HTTPS/8443
    KRBAC->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443
    K8sAPI-->>KRBAC: Authorized
    KRBAC->>APIServer: Forward request<br/>HTTP(S)/8888, PodToPodTLS
    APIServer->>MariaDB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>MySQL/3306, PodToPodTLS
    APIServer->>S3: Store pipeline artifacts<br/>HTTP(S)/9000, S3 credentials
    APIServer-->>KRBAC: Response
    KRBAC-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution
    APIServer->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    Argo->>K8sAPI: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    Argo->>K8sAPI: Create Pipeline Pods<br/>HTTPS/443
    PipelinePod->>APIServer: Report status<br/>HTTP(S)/8888, gRPC/8887
    PipelinePod->>MLMD: Log artifact metadata<br/>gRPC/8080, PodToPodTLS
    PipelinePod->>S3: Upload/download artifacts<br/>HTTP(S)/9000, S3 credentials

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: MLMD Access (External)
    participant EnvoyKRBAC as MLMD Envoy<br/>kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP
    participant Envoy as Envoy Proxy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC
    User->>Router: gRPC request<br/>HTTPS/443
    Router->>EnvoyKRBAC: Reencrypt TLS<br/>HTTPS/8443
    EnvoyKRBAC->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>EnvoyKRBAC: Authorized
    EnvoyKRBAC->>Envoy: Forward<br/>gRPC/9090
    Envoy->>MLMD: Forward<br/>gRPC/8080, PodToPodTLS
    MLMD-->>Envoy: Metadata response
    Envoy-->>EnvoyKRBAC: Response
    EnvoyKRBAC-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: gRPC Response
